<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.5.3">
<l>kālaiyum mālaiyoṟ ṟuṇṭukaṅkul nāḻikai yūḻiyiṉ nīṇṭulāvum</l>
<l>pōlvatōr taṉmaipu kuntuniṟkum poṅkaḻalē yokkumvā ṭaicollil</l>
<l>mālavaṉ māmaṇi vaṇṇaṉmāyam maṟṟumu ḷavavai vantiṭāmuṉ</l>
<l>kōlama yilpayi lumpuṟavil kuṟuṅkuṭik kēyeṉṉai yuyttiṭumiṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Every day is touched by evening; the minutes of darkness</l>
<l rend="indent">creep as long as an eon;</l>
<l>They last, attaining a likeness in [its] quality. If [we] talk of the north wind,</l>
<l rend="indent">it resembles a raging blaze!</l>
<l>The wiles of the dark one, the great jewel-hued one, are on-going;</l>
<l rend="indent">before those can actually occur,</l>
<l>Make sure you take me to Kuṟuṅkuṭi in the woodlands</l>
<l rend="indent">where pretty peacocks prance.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
